      "rationale": "Code verification activities include benchmark comparisons against canonical flow cases and internal consistency checks. Formal MMS verification was not completed for the hemolysis transport sub-model; however, the solver has been widely applied in cardiovascular CFD literature and its numerical implementation is considered well-established. Residual uncertainty from this gap is judged manageable given the Monte Carlo UQ framework applied downstream."
